<P>
National Institute for Dispute Resolution, 1901 L Street NW, #600, Washington, D.C. 20036, (202) 466-4764.
<P>
The Florida Bar, 650 Apalachee Parkway, Tallahassee, FL 32399-2300, (904) 561-5834.

