<H1 ALIGN=CENTER>Alternative Dispute Resolution (ADR) Providers</H1>
The following is a list of some of the ADR providers in Florida, consult
your local telephone directory for others. Some ADR providers specialize
in a particular type of ADR method (e.g., mediation) or a particular type
of dispute (family disputes). Make certain that the ADR provider you retain
has an appropriate level of experience and familiarity with the subject
matter of your dispute. <P>

Dispute Resolution Center<BR>
Supreme Court Building<BR>
Tallahassee, FL 32399-1905<BR>
(904) 921-2910<BR>
Can provide a list of certified mediators in your area.<P>

