The resources in this section have been divided into zones. Resources within each zone have been alphabetized by city.
<P>

Zone 1: 	Northern Florida<BR>
Zone 2: 	East Central Florida<BR>
Zone 3: 	West Central Florida<BR>
Zone 4: 	Southeastern Florida<BR>
Zone 5: 	Southern Florida

<P>
<CENTER><A NAME="10"><H2><B>Hotlines</B></H2></A></CENTER><BR>
Each of the following national and state hotlines serves as a starting point
for acquiring general information and locating related services in a caller's
geographic area. If you are unsure as to which specific services and resources
are right for your needs, these organizations can help you quickly focus
your search in the right direction.
<P>

<P>
<A NAME="20"><H3><B>NATIONAL HOTLINES</B></H3></A>
