<P>
Illinois Department of Revenue, 101 West Jefferson, Springfield, IL 62794, phone: (217) 785-7100; James Thompson Center, Suite Seven, 100 Randolph Street West, Chicago, IL 60601, phone: (312) 814-5232 or toll-free: 1-800-732-8866.
<P>
